[gd_scene format=3 uid="uid://byj1rpsavtewl"]

; Flat-arena variant of MainScene.tscn used by multi-process tests that need a
; large unobstructed floor (e.g. a vehicle pushing cubes for several seconds).
; Shares MainScene.cs as its root script so all server/client hooks, vehicle-
; ownership approver, and --test-harness bootstrap behave identically; the only
; difference from MainScene is the Map subtree — borders/walls/ramps/cylinder/
; offline-ball are gone and the Floor is enlarged to 200×200 so a vehicle has
; room to drive.

